1.10
log
@Oops: confstr()'s return value should include the NUL in its count

Problem pointed out by Andres Perera (andres.p (at) zoho.com)
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: confstr.c,v 1.9 2013/03/01 21:19:42 guenther Exp $ */
/*-
